{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "策展人會客廳", "storyInfo": "在開幕式上，確認了社區居民在朝克里斯達爾藝術館進軍的消息後，上尉宣布一場恐怖襲擊即將發生，並以此為由強行控制了在場的所有人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_021", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_033", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（打哈欠）", "name": "疲憊的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾可真能折磨人，好好的藝術館開幕式，非要放在大晚上舉辦，還說要一直開到天亮。", "name": "疲憊的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信雷內爾一定能給我們看到不一樣的東西，你不也一樣嗎？要不然幹嘛熬這麼晚？", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧。本來想去看街頭藝術社區的藝術狂歡節的，不知道為什麼取消了，我只好來這裡了。", "name": "疲憊的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾的噱頭是真做足了。開幕式的具體安排對我們這樣的高級合作伙伴都要保密……", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，譁眾取寵還是他行啊。", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等你搞出的噱頭能讓全泰拉一大半的藝術投資人都願意像跑到克里斯達爾藝術館一樣跑到我們堡壘山城的總部，那時候再在我耳邊抱怨。", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是……", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宣傳冊上這個卡西米爾人……他的藝術沙龍真能讓我的畫賣出去嗎……", "name": "窘迫的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡可不是萊塔尼亞，一切全看你講的故事夠不夠打動那些投資人。", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你不是說全交給你嗎？", "name": "窘迫的貴族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早跟你說了，染個頭髮，學點髒話，穿身破衣服，自稱腐朽貴族制度的反叛者，好多人都吃這一套，可你又不幹，那我能替你講什麼？", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後再給你個溫馨提示，雖然不如叛逆小子，但落魄貴族這套也有人喜歡。至於能不能打動投資人，就看你臨場發揮了。", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_493_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請各位保持安靜，我們的開幕式馬上就要開始了。", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重複一遍，請各位保持安靜，我們的開幕式，馬上就要開始——", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾信步走上藝術館前廣場上搭設的演講台。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他緩緩掃視了幾次台下的人群，尤其是坐在靠近演講台位置的人，確信該來的人全都來了，然後清了清嗓子。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，早安，午安，晚安——請自行對號入座，這取決於你們慣常的入睡時間。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝鼓掌的各位，也感謝沒鼓掌的各位，你們畢竟犧牲了自己寶貴的睡眠時間，陪我一起觀賞雙日城這場偉大的日出。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼。", "name": "投資界新人"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你們的熱情與期待。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你們願意與我一起創造歷史，儘管只是一小段，在更久遠的跨度下可能微不足道，但對各位來說，必定銘記終身。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好大的口氣。", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g1_dossolesstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天佑玻利瓦爾，天佑多索雷斯♪", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只知道掏錢的遊客腦袋空空♪", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像這座城市的未來♪", "name": "社區居民"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老兄，這個字該換了。你幫我伴奏，我幫你創作點更應景的詞。", "name": "社區歌手"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天佑聯合政府，天佑科瓦爾斯基♪", "name": "社區歌手"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "住在垃圾堆的富豪跟軍頭媾合♪", "name": "社區歌手"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那怪胎著床的夜晚♪", "name": "社區歌手"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，歡迎來到多索雷斯，歡迎來到克里斯達爾藝術館。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在進入正題之前，我希望先介紹給各位一個劃時代的企劃。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信，各位並非全都為了藝術館或開幕式而來——“卡西米爾富二代硬湊起來的噱頭罷了”，想必在座各位也有人是這麼想的。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們大概更關心一個能賺錢的企劃，所以我把它放在前面，滿足你們的好奇心和貪欲。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在場的各位，請讓我看到你們隨身帶著的終端，把它高高舉起。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來各位不光自認為具有高雅的審美品味，都還趕上了時代的潮流。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "便攜終端，多麼偉大的發明，讓人擺脫消磨時光的罪惡感，帶來城市各個角落的消息，把整座城市連結在一起。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我願意為這座未來的富礦添上一座以藝術為名的鑽探平台，讓其中湧出的金幣和紙鈔填滿你們的腰包。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隆重為各位介紹這項突破性的發明，即將在城際網路上掀起浪潮的……", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虛擬藝術藏品專案。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g1_dossolesstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老哥，我怎麼沒見過你？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼可能沒見過我？我就住你家樓上！", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你是那個……皮斯托？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對對對。", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你不是去治病了嗎？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去治病怎麼了，去治病雷內爾就有權進我們社區搞破壞嗎？", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得好！", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，等到了藝術館，準不準備大幹一場？", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然要大幹一場！", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就對了！對這種人不能有一點同情心！", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虛擬藝術藏品？我們給你投資是要看這種東西嗎？", "name": "投資界新人"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，想想看，一部分藝術家以後不再和顏料、畫筆打交道，他們在終端前為城際網路創造的作品同樣能成為你們的投資對象。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我把藝術館中收藏的某幅畫作在城際網路上原樣複製，諸位隨時可以在終端上看到畫作的每一個細節。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒人可以奪走或複製這幅畫，你擁有處置這幅虛擬畫作的全部權利，想賣，想毀，全由你自己決定——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這是對藝術的褻瀆！", "name": "投資界新人"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說我褻瀆藝術？看看你身邊那位大腹便便的投資界前輩，他才是褻瀆藝術的大師。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們根本不關注創作者的想法和表達，你們只想把所有解釋的權力握在自己手裡，好方便你們根據行情操縱藝術品價格。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也在做這種事，你父親也在做這種事！", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我什麼時候說斯特凡·科瓦爾斯基沒有褻瀆藝術了？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不用看就知道，你身邊那位看起來唯唯諾諾的人，不就正求著你請人褻瀆他的藝術，好換一筆錢嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#3$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#3$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……瘋子。", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟觀眾吵架也是他開幕式的一環？", "name": "疲憊的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正他是以標新立異聞名的，誰又敢說不是呢？先生，你說呢？", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁，無聊的傢伙，就只知道玩終端。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）果然這群傢伙也不是什麼好東西。虛偽。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉掩去眼底的凶光，換上了一副漠然的表情，以免在此刻被人看出端倪。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位，接下來我要向各位介紹整個泰拉的第一批虛擬藝術藏品。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "演講台下的人群暫時靜了下來。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們已經領教了雷內爾的不可理喻，但一個不可理喻的人也是人，也想維持自己現有的優越生活，換句話說，也需要錢。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差別只不過是，遵守規則的正常人會用大家都能接受的方法和和氣氣地賺錢，而不可理喻的人總想在賺錢的同時鄙視其他人。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是不要緊，只要他還想要錢，正常人總能找到機會，把那個瘋子的內裡瓜分乾淨。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）恩師，我們這下怎麼辦？", "name": "投資界新人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）靜觀其變。", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）看看他能給我們做什麼藏品出來。", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）城際網路不足以支持一個新的投資領域，但這個瘋子說不定真能挖到什麼寶。", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）反正我們有的是辦法拿到我們想要的。", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些藏品飽含著我這段時間在多索雷斯感受到的善意與誠實，光明與美好，因而具有無與倫比的紀念意義。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我向各位隆重推出——“煩人上尉”！！", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#3$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlight", "channel": "1", "Delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "48_i03", "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……這有什麼價值？", "name": "投資界新人"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個瘋子，精神錯亂的富家少爺！", "name": "傲慢的掮客"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完了，全完了，這還能辦起什麼藝術沙龍。我還怎麼賣畫……", "name": "窘迫的貴族"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等等，老兄，雷內爾那批虛擬藏品的原型……是你？", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？", "name": "馬特奧"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉站起身，先是看了看手裡的終端，然後看了看顯示器，最後和雷內爾視線相接。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬特奧上尉，鑑於我們第一次打交道的經歷是如此愉快，我再送你一份禮物。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將成為泰拉有史以來第一批虛擬藝術藏品的原型。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，在其中挑一個，我願意將其免費贈予你。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全場的視線都集中在上尉身上。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉沒有第一時間回答雷內爾，只是先看了一眼終端。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於，他看見了自己一直在等的消息。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，雷內爾先生，你留著自己用吧。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，各位，但我有一個緊急消息要在這裡宣布。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是誰？", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是玻利瓦爾聯合政府派駐多索雷斯的代表，先生。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據我們得到的最新消息，一場針對藝術館的恐怖攻擊即將發生。希望各位能聽從指示有序避難。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據可靠消息，暴徒正往這裡趕來，請各位在我手下士兵的引導下進入藝術館避難。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地平線處，有不少模模糊糊的人影似乎正朝藝術館湧來，人影聚集處甚至還隱約飄來了雜亂的歌聲。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，大老爺。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！我要找坎黛拉——", "name": "投資界前輩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可不行，喂，你，把他拖走。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "軍官的手下"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，雷內爾。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬特奧先生，你真是為我的開幕式增添了一個巨大的驚喜——", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來人，把他給我拖走，拖到他最喜歡的陽台上去看日出，我等一下再去找他聊聊。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，還有，記得讓他自己爬樓梯。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況如何？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大多數人都被我們嚇住——不，都接受我們的安排，正在往克里斯達爾藝術館內部轉移。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有幾個不配合的人不願意聽我們的，您看……", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不配合？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等大多數人都進來了，把刀架在他們脖子上，看看他們還配不配合。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街頭藝術社區那群人呢？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有幾分鐘就到。我們安插在其中的人已經成功把他們煽動起來，只等他們到廣場上撒野，把恐怖攻擊的名義坐實了。", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……天就要亮了，我們得趕快。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g1_dossolesstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轉過前面那個彎，我們就到藝術館了！", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，我等不及要給雷內爾來點震撼了。", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好！把他的藝術館砸爛，把他那些破玩意搶光！", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想什麼呢？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我想什麼了？不是說好了要大幹一場嗎？", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說的大幹一場是要在藝術館門口搞我們的藝術節，讓雷內爾徹底抬不起頭，你說的大幹一場是什麼？", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，我先去前面看看狀況！", "name": "狡猾的陌生人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾！", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛有個傢伙說是住我樓上的，有點可疑——", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後呢？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "社區小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼了？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小販張大了嘴，用手指向一個轉角之隔的藝術館前廣場。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廣場上雖有演講台，有座位，甚至有觀客留在椅子上的外套……"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是一個人都沒有。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個都沒有。"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}